N. Robert Hammer 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer at COMMVAULT SYSTEMS INC, N. Robert Hammer  made $7,333,692 in total compensation.  Of this total $619,000 was received as a salary, $872,970 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $5,736,338 was awarded as stock and $105,384 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2017 fiscal year. 


